          "documentation": "# anvi-export-gene-clusters\n\nExport gene clusters in a pan-db as a three-column, TAB-delimited file that associates each gene call in each genome with a gene cluster.\n\n🔙 To the main page of anvi’o programs and artifacts.\n\n## Authors\n\n## Can consume\n\npan-db \n\n## Can provide\n\ngene-clusters-txt \n\n## Usage\n\nNo one has described the usage of this program :/ If you would like to contribute, please see previous examples here , and feel free to add a Markdown formatted file in that directory named “anvi-export-gene-clusters.md”. For a template, you can use the markdown file for `anvi-gen-contigs-database`. THANK YOU!\n\n## Additional Resources\n\nAre you aware of resources that may help users better understand the utility of this program? Please feel free to edit this file on GitHub. If you are not sure how to do that, find the `__resources__` tag in this file to see an example."
