          "id": "anvi-export-splits-and-coverages",
          "kind": "program",
          "title": "anvi-export-splits-and-coverages",
          "command": "anvi-export-splits-and-coverages",
          "description": "Export split or contig sequences and coverages across samples stored in an anvi'o profile database. This program is especially useful if you would like to 'bin' your splits or contigs outside of anvi'o and import the binning results into anvi'o using anvi-import-collection program",
