          "description": "A tRNA-seq database contains information on tRNA sequences predicted from a single tRNA-seq sample . This database is the key output of anvi-trnaseq . That program predicts which reads are tRNA through structural profiling, clusters tRNA reads into discrete biological sequences, and predicts the positions of nucleotide modifications.",
          "version": "main",
