          "id": "trnaseq-fasta",
          "kind": "data",
          "title": "trnaseq-fasta",
          "artifactType": "FASTA",
          "description": "A trnaseq-fasta is a fasta file of sequences from a single tRNA-seq sample of split that is suitable to be used by anvi-trnaseq to create a trnaseq-db . Like contigs-fasta files, this file is required to have simple deflines . Take a look at your deflines prior to mapping, and remove anything that is not a digit, an ASCII letter, an underscore, or a dash character. The program anvi-script-reformat-fasta can do this automatically for you with the flag --simplify-names .",
          "version": "main",
          "requires": [],
          "provides": [],
