          "artifactType": "TXT",
          "description": "The output of anvi-summarize-blitz . anvi-summarize-blitz summarizes read-recruitment statistics for a collection of bins across multiple samples. It produces long format output in which each row contains the (weighted) average statistics of a bin in a sample. Each statistic is summarized in a different column of the file.",
          "version": "main",
          "requires": [],
          "provides": [],
          "parameters": [],
